longBusinessSummary: Steed Oriental (Holdings) Company Limited, an investment holding company, sources, manufactures, and sells plywood and other wooden products in Hong Kong and the People's Republic of China. It offers structural panels; supplementary materials used in construction; and wooden doors and windows, structural components, furniture, and others. Steed Oriental (Holdings) Company Limited was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.
